dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Waupaca County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2018, includes the layers 'Waupaca_Hydro_2018_Arc' and 'Waupaca_Hydro_2018_Poly'.
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2019. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2018. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2019. This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data for this county, please visit: https://data2017-04-05t135915451z-waupacacounty.opendata.arcgis.com/
